message.body: How are you and where are you from?
I'm in a Philly suburb with my family for the weekend. My sister and I are about to cook a Philippine dessert. :)
thats so cool!!! I lived in philly about 2yrs ago. I good thank you. Im celebrating my sisters birthday. Im in California. We just ate Thai food
Ooh nice! My other sister is visiting California for a short vacation right now. She's in san Diego. Happy birthday to your sister!
Have you participated in other penn language lab studies?
The last time I participated, I had to take or make calls, with half of them being from a noisy environment!
